<D>__{what’s your name?}
<C>__{black girl}
<D>__{tisha.}
<C>__{derek}
<D>__{how old are you, tisha?}
<A>__{she holds up four fingers. derek smiles.}
<C>__{black mother}
<P>__{(staring at derek)}
<D>__{come here, tisha.}
<A>__{tisha return to her mother and they exit. derek watches the girl as she continues to stare at him, wide eyed. outside, they hear screeching tires and a blue ford pulls up in front. rasmussen and young fuhrman get out.}
